00:16:33.672 --> 00:16:37.132
Individuals such as myself require precise

346
00:16:37.172 --> 00:16:40.672
information to calculate insulin dosage

347
00:16:40.732 --> 00:16:44.632
correctly to avoid not only immediate risk and

348
00:16:44.672 --> 00:16:48.612
